4bdb3a7cfbc31584be377fbf","tid":6503,"uid":21137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:19:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/201858_4c2375ca84f0d562b5a4000a05514e2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F201858_4c2375ca84f0d562b5a4000a05514e2d.jpg&h=7ab7b3eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce45da2268d02f06909795be9d289caf46b28e3e","tid":6503,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我思疑全部都係新會然</blockquote><br />\n我屌你老母死肥西真係戇撚鳩鳩無得食賓周<br />\n我唔該你認清一個事實就係 你條肥西有拖拍係奇蹟 無拖拍係正常既<br />\n你憑著80幾kg既身軀都有仔溝過你應該要知足、感恩<br />\n你比人飛根本係遲早既事 唔該認清事實<br />\n你ex當初可能係盲撚左又或者係悶悶地想食下肥膩野先試下你<br />\n所以唔撚好日撚日打埋d嬌情文 又share d港女語錄係度叫春啦<br />\n好撚嘔心真係 肥婆係度扮小女人扮嬌情 好撚核突<br />\n你d朋友比面你會like下 你d好姊妹驚你唔開心會安慰下你<br />\n但其實人地背後已經暗地笑鳩緊你肥西失戀狂叫春 係咪破唔到處所以覺得唔甘心呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嘔撚心無d自知之明 死肥西"},{"pid":"b34a8a8c47df5d2eccf3b37d46ec300bfb1c48e1","tid":6503,"uid":8329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:38:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"574d9f8fbea52edca501828539a9b8867305c995","tid":6503,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:03:58.000Z","msg":"attention whore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bddd71dee9e6b70dfb8d05a11c22ed36c04dfaf0","tid":6503,"uid":24672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf80837c688709563601c58c46ed673aeb1fa784","tid":6503,"uid":10620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f869f67c13a15813f84d8d7fcccc2dac81a0c4","